---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro';
import AddressSearch from '../components/AddressSearch.vue';
---

<Layout title="Who owns Philly">
	<main class="flex flex-col items-center h-screen lg:pt-24 p-4">
		<h1 class="text-4xl text-bold text-emerald-800 mb-2">Who Owns Philly?</h1>
		<p class="text-center"> Find out who owns what in Philly, what else
			they might own in the city, and information about their properties.</p>

		<div class="py-8 flex w-full lg:w-1/2 flex-col items-center">
			<AddressSearch client:load/>
			<div class="text-center mt-2 text-xs lg:text-sm">
				Enter a <b>Philly address</b>, <b>landlord's name</b>, or <b>property manager</b>.
			</div>
			<p class="text-center mt-2 text-xs lg:text-sm">
				<b>Is the address not showing up?</b> Search for the address on
				<a target="_blank" href="https://atlas.phila.gov">atlas.phila.gov</a> to see how the
				City formats addresses and owner names. We try our best to match
				addresses to the Cityâ€™s format, but sometimes the City formats addresses
				in ways we can't detect.
			</p>

		</div>
		<div class="w-full">
			<div class="ml-2 mb-4">View sample owner properties</div>
			<ul class="w-full flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between gap-4">
				<li class="border flex flex-col justify-between lg:w-1/3">
					<a href="/properties/032022200/summary" class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
						<div class="p-4 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-between ">
							<div>Odin Properties</div>
							<div class="text-gray-400">1200 Callowhill St Suite 403</div>
							<div class="mt-2 text-black">Odin Properties was founded in 2009 by real estate investor Philip Balderston. Balderston left Tower Investments (Bart Blatstein) after the foreclosure crisis to buy distressed properties in Philadelphia.</div>
						</div>
						<div class="text-gray-400 border-t p-2">~470 Properties</div>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="border lg:w-1/3">
					<a href="/properties/871288650/summary" class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
						<div class="p-4 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-between ">
							<div>Allan Domb Realty</div>
							<div class="text-gray-400">1845 Walnut St Suite 2200</div>
							<div class="mt-2 text-black"> 1845 Walnut is a large office building on Rittenhouse Square with many suites, and several suites are associated with realty companies...</div>
						</div>
						<div class="text-gray-400 border-t p-2">~470 Properties</div>
					</a>
				</li>
				<li class="border lg:w-1/3">
					<a href="/properties/888058983/summary" class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
						<div class="p-4 rounded-md flex flex-col justify-between ">
							<div>Pearl Properties</div>
							<div class="text-gray-400">110 S 19th St Suite 300</div>
							<div class="mt-2 text-black"> Pearl Properties works in real estate development, construction,
								residential leasing, and property management. Multiple LLCs receive
								mail to Pearl Properties' office, including 14 WA Partners LP,
								associated with 1401 Walnut - Pearl Apartments.</div></div>
						<div class="text-gray-400 border-t p-2">~470 Properties</div>
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>

		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
